This project vendors and adapts third-party MIT-licensed material. Their
copyright notices and license terms are reproduced verbatim in CREDITS.md and
in .claude/NOTICE.md, as the MIT License requires.

  - everything-claude-unity (XeldarAlz) — vendored at v1.5.0. Most of .claude/
    and the repo's scripts/, tests/, docs/, examples/, and templates/ derive
    from it.
  - Claude-Code-Game-Studios (Donchitos) — adapted. The design/production
    agents, commands, and templates derive from it; each carries an inline
    attribution comment.

provenance.tsv records, per file, which upstream it came from and whether it
was modified. .claude/NOTICE.md ships into installed projects so the notices
travel with the copies, as the license requires.
